branchCategory.name: Auto Switches
branchCategory.description: <p>Auto switches on actuators and air grippers for sensing the end of stroke. Solid state type switches are included with a pre-wired connector and two color indication light. Reed switches have lead wire and indicator light option.  Made from materials compatible with secondary battery manufacturing.</p>
